Conclusion
In this lab, you successfully:

Installed EvtxECmd on Linux for Windows Event Log analysis
Parsed EVTX files into readable CSV format for investigation
Analyzed logon and logoff events to identify patterns and anomalies
Detected suspicious activities including failed logon attempts and unusual access patterns
